<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Student Activity Tracker</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>

<body>

<header>
<h1>Student Activity Tracker</h1>
<p>Track your daily learning activities</p>
</header>

<div class="container">

<h2>Your Activities</h2>

<ul id="activityList">

<li>
<h3>HTML Practice</h3>
<p>Complete basic HTML exercises</p>
<button onclick="markComplete(this)">Mark Completed</button>
<span class="status">Pending</span>
</li>

<li>
<h3>CSS Styling</h3>
<p>Practice designing web pages</p>
<button onclick="markComplete(this)">Mark Completed</button>
<span class="status">Pending</span>
</li>

<li>
<h3>JavaScript Basics</h3>
<p>Learn variables and functions</p>
<button onclick="markComplete(this)">Mark Completed</button>
<span class="status">Pending</span>
</li>

<li>
<h3>Mini Project</h3>
<p>Create a simple webpage project</p>
<button onclick="markComplete(this)">Mark Completed</button>
<span class="status">Pending</span>
</li>

<li>
<h3>Debugging Practice</h3>
<p>Fix errors in sample programs</p>
<button onclick="markComplete(this)">Mark Completed</button>
<span class="status">Pending</span>
</li>

<li>
<h3>Assignment Submission</h3>
<p>Submit completed assignment</p>
<button onclick="markComplete(this)">Mark Completed</button>
<span class="status">Pending</span>
</li>

</ul>

<h2 id="progress">Progress: 0 out of 6 activities completed</h2>

</div>

<script src="script.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
